summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Forward Thrust Park Plan and Program; making a determination pursuant to Section 5 of King County Resolution 34571 that the project identified as "O.O. Denny Youth Camp Improvements" set forth at Section 3.1 (1) of said Resolution is impractical to substantially accomplish and abandoning that project and authorizing allocation of bond proceeds made available by such abandonment, along with other associated funds, to the completion, expansion, enlargement, extension or additional development of other projects set forth and authorized in Section 3 of King County Resolution 34571.
